changeSet.sql: INSERT INTO PERFIL_PERMISSAO (ID_PERFIL, ID_PERMISSAO) (SELECT PERFIL.ID, PERMISSAO.ID FROM PERFIL PERFIL, PERMISSAO PERMISSAO)

changeSet.sql: UPDATE USUARIO SET LOGIN = ID WHERE LOGIN IS NULL

changeSet.author: rodolpho.couto
changeSet.sql: UPDATE USUARIO SET LOGIN = ID WHERE (SELECT COUNT(0) FROM USUARIO USU WHERE USU.LOGIN = USUARIO.LOGIN) > 1

changeSet.sql: INSERT INTO FERIADO_AUD (ID, DESCRICAO, ANO, MES, DIA, ID_AUD, TIPO_AUD) SELECT ID, DESCRICAO, ANO, MES, DIA, (SELECT MIN(ID) FROM LOG_AUDITORIA), 0 AS TIPO_AUD FROM FERIADO
